.";i:52;s:95:"If the remotes and keypad still have the same problem the logic board will need to be replaced.";i:53;s:103:"Look under the garage door opener light cover on the same side as the antenna to find the LEARN button.";i:54;s:145:"Garage Door Opener Remote Compatibility Chart Select from a range of LiftMaster remote controls that are compatible with your garage door opener.";i:55;s:96:"Theres a big chance your garage door remote is not working consistently because of faulty wires.";i:56;s:64:"Check the quality of the garage openers wiring with these steps.";i:57;s:68:"Unplug the automatic opener and disconnect the wires from the motor.";i:58;s:41:"Reconnect the opener to the power source.";i:59;s:62:"Clear the openers memories and reprogram the remotes controls.";}}